獲獎紀錄：




Distinguished Teaching Award II, 2012, National Chung-Hsing University 
The Best Award of Articles, Dec. 6th, 2014, The Rural Economics Society of Taiwan, Analysis of Trade Patterns and Duration: Evidence from Food Industries between the OECD Countries
國際貿易類佳作,Nov.27th,2015,2015 10th CABMT Annual Conference, 紅色供應鏈之存活期間分析
科技部指導大專學生研究計畫榮獲104年度研究創作獎




 






研究領域：




經濟整合中貿易型態變化的經濟分析
農產貿易障礙的經濟分析




 






博士論文：



            Ph.D. Dissertation The Determinants of Agricultural Trade patterns: East Asia Perspectives, Department of Agricultural and Resource Economics, The University of Tokyo, March 2008, pp. 123. Journal Publications


 








